<br>
I could list a lot of pros and a couple cons, but I'll be brief... much lower downtime, more exciting combat since it's possible to take multiple mobs without relying on mez.  Less dependency on specific classes to get shit done.  Every class can solo at least decently, and some can do it really well.  Most of the really good gear is made by player tradeskills (some would consider this a con, but not me).  The races are all really cool, the classes rock, and Hibernia &gt; all.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Ahry - firbolg hero, Percival server <BR>
Arikel Callistrae - retired
monk of the Erollisi Marr server
