I am an armsman for example. Armsmen get 2x spec points for every level (IE at level 40 I gain 80 spec points). This is enough to max out two skills.<br>
Now, I can max two skills, but how many do I get? 7<br>
What do I do? well specialize! (as the spec points suggest)<br>
If I wanted to be a total tank I'd max both Shield and Parry, but that'd be pretty damn boring now wouldn't it? =D<br>
Instead I've opted to max Polearm since it is a skill unique to the armsman, and to get both Parry and Slashing into the mid 30's. <p><a href="mailto:yang@monkly-business.com">
