None of eq's 'pray that pixel doen't poof my arrow', or 'z-axis attacks are an exploit, archers can no longer stand on a ridge and fire down onto people.' <br>
<br>
Archers get bow spec, which gives you the critical shot (as I understand it). At max range, you can land a crit shot and still have time to nock and fire another 2 arrows at the incoming monster, leaving it at or below 1/2 health when it reaches you.<br>
<br>
